THE END
The party has successfully navigated social intrigue, infiltration, and potentially combat to acquire what they needed. They've crossed into Whiterun Hold with a suspicious Thalmor emissary who now knows their faces.
The hunt for the real Obsidian Lanterns continues.
But Rulindil remembers. And the Aldmeri Dominion has a very, very long memory.


